title: ISic001686. I.Sicily inscription 001686
body:
Facsimile Images

1[---]·TORI
2[---]PERAUG
3[---]O

Apparatus criticus

Text after autopsy; Orsi: [impera]tori; but the trace before the T is not easily compatible with A, and more like the foot of L, E, or C.

translation

commentary

Manganaro (Epigraphica 1989, p.181, no. 59) published the text on the other side (ISic000726) without noting the existence of this text on the reverse, published by Orsi.

bibliography

  • Orsi NSA 1920 312 https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392
